          <Vi>Hơn nữa, hơn thế nữa, hơn nữa còn</Vi>
          <En>Used to introduce a further point or argument that supports or adds to what has already been said.</En>
          <Example>In addition to the environmental benefits, the project reduces costs; moreover, it improves public health.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
